elements.name: As a user I want to update and publish post

steps.name: I enter "l.solier@uniandes.edu.co" into input field having name attribute "identification"
I enter "Lui$$olier15" into input field having name attribute "password"
I click on element having css selector "button.login"
I click on element having css selector "[href="#/posts/"]"
I click on element number "0" having css selector "li.gh-posts-list-item" of list having css selector "ol.posts-list"
I clean input field having css selector "textarea.gh-editor-title"
I enter "Titulo actualizando usando Kraken" into input field having css selector "textarea.gh-editor-title"
I enter "Descripcion actualizando usando Kraken" into input field having css selector "div[data-kg=editor]"
I click on element having css selector "div.gh-publishmenu-trigger"
I click on element having css selector "button.gh-publishmenu-button"
I click on element having css selector "[href="#/posts/"]"
I should see text "Titulo actualizando usando Kraken"
